      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and reflects its age and mileage through honest wear. The exterior paint shows its history with several noticeable scratches, a few small door dings, and some fading on the roof. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows significant wear and some staining on the carpets. Mechanically, it starts and runs reliably, though it may require some routine maintenance and minor repairs in the near future to keep it in top shape. It is a solid choice for someone looking for a dependable budget vehicle who doesn't mind some cosmetic imperfections.",
