    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, she\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super dependable for all my commutes and weekend getaways. There\u2019s a little bit of normal wear and tear here and there, but it still looks great and runs even better! I\u2019ve really stayed on top of the upkeep, and I\u2019m looking for someone who will enjoy it just as much as I have. Feel free to reach out if you want to come by and take it for a spin!",
