    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 2004 Porsche 911 Carrera (996.2) features the refined 3.6L naturally aspirated flat-six engine, delivering 320 hp through a precise 6-speed longitudinal manual transaxle. The M96 powerplant has been meticulously cared for, featuring a documented IMS bearing retrofit and recent cooling system overhaul to ensure thermal efficiency. The chassis maintains excellent torsional rigidity, supported by a McPherson strut front and multi-link rear suspension geometry that offers communicative feedback and sharp turn-in. Finished in Arctic Silver, the paint retains a deep luster with only minor road-surface peppering, while the interior exhibits a light patina consistent with a well-loved driver. This example offers a purely mechanical driving experience with hydraulic power steering and a linear power band that rewards high-RPM engagement.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 32
    },
    {
