    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained luxury SUV offers a perfect balance of performance and daily utility. The exterior retains a brilliant, deep luster, though a close inspection reveals a few minor stone chips on the front fascia consistent with regular highway use. Inside, the cabin remains a smoke-free sanctuary; the premium leather upholstery is supple, showing only light natural creasing on the driver\u2019s side bolster. Every electronic feature, from the panoramic sunroof to the high-fidelity sound system, operates flawlessly. Under the hood, the engine runs smooth and quiet, backed by a comprehensive service history and a recent professional fluid service. With four matching high-performance tires and a clean undercarriage, this vehicle is mechanically sound and ready for the road. It is a reliable, sophisticated choice for a buyer who appreciates a car that has been truly respected and cared for.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
